formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1	Value of Cost of land shown as notional cost, which are calculated based on Jantri 		Rate.
2	Based on record of cost incurred maintained by the promoter, we have reported the 		above cost like of Sr. Number (ii) b already included in sr. (ii)  a(ii) and a(iii).
3	Regarding Rera Bank account :
		a)	Promoter have given Rera bank details at the time of 						registration are of bank of baroda via account number 						02590200001475. But actually the promoter have deposited the all 				money received from the alllotee are in above mentioned icici 					bank hence we have mentioned that bank details as Rera bank 					details herein above.
		b)	Moreover, Promoter have not maintained separate Rera bank 					account for the separate (each) project however promoter have 				maintained the such separate bank account based on government scheme 			wise like Pradhan mantri aavas yojna PMAY, Mukhya mantri aavas yojna 			(MMAY) etc.  
4	We have mentioned the 100 % amount received from the allotee in raw number (7) 	regarding amount withdrawn.
5	We have mentioned the value per unit for the allotee as excluding the amount of 	assistance of Rs.1,50,000/- from the GOI and Rs.1,50,000/- from the GOG  i.e Combined 	Rs.3,00,000/- . in short to say, unit value shown is of actual deal value receivable from the 	allottee and such value also mentioned in the allotment letter and sale deed of the allottee.
